summary:
Energetic, enthusiastic, focused - I like propagating these to the team to deliver on time while enjoying the work and the good results. 
My professional interests range from technology, innovation and technology transfer,  renewable energies and stakeholder management; I am balancing those with a strong technical background (PhD in Geophysics).
I have a particular interest in gender balance, inclusiveness and avid believer in diverse team power. I have been on the board of various networks since university years, part of professional networks with focus on gender balance and recently helped launch 75inQ (www.75inQ.com), a company focusing in bringing focus on ambitious women and new energies world. 

I am stress-resilient; I strive to simplify processes/workflows and avoid time-wasting on nonsense and useless acts. There; I said it.
